{"h46fb52d1g7dc2g4c36g8831g574ff82a492f": ["*The corpse lets out an angry hiss of foul air, then goes silent.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "ea5d38aa-58a2-475a-0465-15dd01026a18"], "h9d679b5fg20eag4bf0g907dg7a4706fafa38": ["*The dead goblin is silent. Even magic cannot coax more words from him.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "297a8b4a-11b8-b057-eef7-96256ec04414"], "h0cbf7acfg75f8g4541g84b3g4fc668044a1a": ["*The goblin's corpse grunts and spasms.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "d1a46fb2-3b3c-9cc4-b4bc-33c89d60e90f"], "h1bc2f148ga939g48a8g9f4bg9126007bc1df": ["I'll apologise later - this one's mine.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "c4264016-b446-d954-7ee7-a722aa27b4a4"], "had1ef9cfgd868g48a4gaeb4gabc4392c9a83": ["Be my guest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "97fe886c-cf9e-441e-2c8d-5dc99e7f4aa8"], "hd22c493cgdf8cg4cc3gaa67g94b1f561d6ac": ["Mizora - the woman taken from your camp. <i>Where is she?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "1737f00a-80ee-099b-e320-580b81d1fac3"], "hfebd6da5g945dg4958g84fbg2f1cef769745": ["... gone... taken to the shadows...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "446bbb88-0149-655f-da4b-9a1d235c86fe"], "h6a29fe80g0d32g4f33g8eacgbfb970a0d890": ["Not good enough. Show me where!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "909be7ac-9fe5-7d1b-adf9-a896c4b60a44"], "h31007012gacc7g4d0fgb143g74bd7d0c7258": ["North road... Moonrise towers... the drow...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "489ad155-929e-7696-4854-dcc17bc62ab1"], "h8f48b6ceg11fcg481eg9a62g9724839bd95d": ["*You are left with memories - not yours, but Wyll's. First, a bloodbath; then, a promise.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "7ea57f12-7716-8a6e-1954-763f4336323f"], "h26c1e7cdg3bceg4823g8c8bg4497e04447be": ["Moonrise Towers...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "2bf5ba30-0d8f-cc0e-ad37-fb38b4a6661c"], "h1c3ad9a7ge83dg4a6fg8969gbe223e3196eb": ["Come on. We need to get moving.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "5acfa72a-7cb5-e8fe-0ca6-e90d42dfe3bc"], "hf26e6096ga3c8g4101g9ffeg33aa0018d8b6": ["Spike. <i>Where is he?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "e32cef37-8a3c-f785-d652-c49ecea963c7"], "h40ac5b09g26f4g4a48gaa4bg55d1cededc3e": ["Spike... camp... torturin'... prisoners...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "8599966e-b7c7-56c5-5f3d-0ffe21dc03b1"], "h111a543fg09e4g4517ga172gcb5de4152276": ["Not good enough. Show me where!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "174e1845-60f2-c0f0-5a6b-c1839781551e"], "hbdd20e4bg5733g4d91gadcbg59cc2cc3c9d6": ["East... whole camp o' goblins... feastin'...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "51d7e75b-add0-a1c4-9a4f-3a4b3df6289b"], "h264a04bbg1becg4893g890ege32ea2d9f5ae": ["Come on. We need to get moving.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "f2243832-65aa-e9c7-be05-1bce0ba3312d"], "h3b509c1ag2506g4f9ag8f45g7da8addfdecb": ["Wrong - it's <i>mine</i>. Find your own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "8dfe5910-f9e8-34bc-6608-08a547376fd5"], "h8d74f487g244fg4028g92efgf3be9b6f8e86": ["Damn you. What more can be taken from me?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "f74f0adb-e6b1-d42a-94cf-fb528247ef97"], "h9b06d5cdgc388g4c3ag83e6g476d45d83ca5": ["*The corpse lets out an angry hiss of foul air, then goes silent.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "306f0d4c-857f-fe74-fe73-78288564a8af"], "hd1eed7bcg7a6fg4c6egac94g29a2d1526d29": ["Top work, chief. The cream truly rises.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "398a48ba-5315-fc4f-0aea-fcd79afd08e4"], "he63af02cg93c2g4372ga8d6g67e2f84fbfc4": ["Urgh... <i>cold</i>...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "e9acb114-f890-613d-fdae-dd06ee811aec"], "ha41ff7f3ga5b5g42dbgae6dge73c4dc50862": ["Who were you in life?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "baf3bba7-a734-fabb-93db-8acab1e7039b"], "h81c93b64g358fg4c6bg9475g957c33a30f92": ["Fezzerk... best raider... east o' the... Sea o' Swords...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "3c7906e9-a45a-85a5-e14d-24edc9230305"], "hf3dc4313gce2cg4103g92f6g2854e46ad81a": ["What were you doing here?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "78387d4a-0fa6-659d-6e49-58d75a233125"], "h41d4e3f4g2c60g45f5g8eeeg17b4b9129327": ["Hostages... the Absolute wants... <i>hostages</i>...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "28f5a1b5-844a-c0f2-c7ce-b64b8b6d78f0"], "h5f7aa5a9g74d3g4316ga80eg1603717297f8": ["Tell me where you kept your valuables.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "6a83714e-62f4-8a20-75dd-cdbe8b4d05d4"], "h1eaa90cegd2ffg43ecg9c02gd9957bed1401": ["No... valuables... only... hostages...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "28863bc1-5bad-a569-c533-48bf751d0232"], "h97eb79deg1868g44b6g9c41g059a518aad68": ["Who killed you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "cc376b52-8c5b-bf65-030f-5add219fae47"], "h4349624fgb111g4d7cg87e4gc6198abced95": ["Coward... attacked...  interrupted my work... ", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "cebebd4a-3b86-a5a6-214e-04f4276a2ded"], "h80ef75d9g1d82g4706ga2abg7ce55ca0f345": ["Where did you come from?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "40e3fbe7-cf8e-0fdb-3e1f-3b072e8c87ca"], "hbba4b318g1126g48f5gb6ebgc000d433f176": ["The... <i>towers...</i>", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "aee3fd0d-2efe-86ff-2894-1de5f379e0ef"], "h90836d0fg89efg4578g8358g8f5a7d329340": ["Who do you answer to?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "a289d1d7-c2b4-d7c1-25a0-0352e611ee6a"], "h8d19f5fcg6422g418cgadb0gdbfce47d7ed3": ["The... Absolute... she... chose us...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "88a4307d-de57-3a5c-5438-f4189ce87559"], "h37051faag663cg4c4dgba00g2eb0b2e4a48e": ["Are there more like you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "b67db9d0-0d75-ce57-f0be-6882010ec135"], "h862a48f5g5024g4fc8g8687g9bf1b159e4dc": ["Many... so many... legions o' goblins... an' more... serving... the Absolute...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "cf5df04c-cb57-2ae8-a2a1-083eefd22764"], "hc818a261g8c52g4d13ga0dfgadcb4c76d8ad": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "b1de149f-fb8e-5baf-2668-ebeedd67888d"], "hb8d8ce01g4bdbg418cgb50dg9398e2e63f39": ["*The dead goblin speaks no more. You take your leave.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "bef5ad35-1b58-38d1-a546-48aba2dfe892"], "h9ff51dbfg5354g4522g96fdg1f9739ac192a": ["Forget the corpse. We're done here.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "56637ded-b537-20ae-d268-f0e6a4f2abe1"], "h41885062g1479g48e3gaf9eg934c4f71bbd8": ["Damn you. What more can be taken from me?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Companions\\Origin_Moments\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Dead_OM_Wyll_COM.html", "8fd29045-bbfd-d36a-99f3-9db2e2835095"]}